room_title: Escape room "Depths of Osiris VR" by Time Travel Escapes in West Palm Beach
room_description: We need a team of specialists to help us.  Our team of deep sea archeologists have been stumped for months after discovering the lost Temple of Osiris. We need you and your team to help us gain access to the temple and retrieve the rumored artifact inside. You have limited oxygen so act fast and help us with this mission.
